# 🧭 2. Routing (CRITICAL)

Define proper navigation using `$routeProvider`:

- dalogin-quarkus/README.md
- mbooks-quarkus/README.md
- mbook-quarkus/README.md

Ensure:

* Default route → `/login`
* No broken routes
* Parameters always passed correctly

---

# 🔄 3. Application Flow

```
Login
  ↓
Movies
  ↓
Venues (by movie)
  ↓
Date (by venue)
  ↓
Seats (by date)
  ↓
Booking
```

---

