- dalogin-quarkus/README.md
- mbooks-quarkus/README.md
- mbook-quarkus/README.md

## 4.4 StateService (NEW)

Stores for Basket:

* selectedSeats

---

# 🧠 5. Controllers Responsibilities

## LoginController

* handle login
* redirect to landing page

## MoviesController

* load movies
* select movie → route to venues

## VenueController

* load venues
* select venue → route to seats

## BookingController

* load seats
* manage seat selection
* confirm booking

## ImageController

* load movie posters
* handle image errors

---

# 🎨 6. UI Templates

Film-Review-Movie-Database

The current satet is capable to lead the user through the booking flow, but the UI needs improvement. We need to:

- make design consistent across pages
- ensure all necessary elements are present
- fix any broken UI components into kubernetes

## login.html

* username/password inputs
* login button
* change password link

## movies.html

* movie list/grid
* poster + title

## venues.html

* list of venues
* show name, address, times
* select date from drop down → navigate to seats

## seats.html

* seat grid
* selectable seats:

  * available
  * selected
  * taken

## booking.html

* summary view
* confirm booking button

